All Classes

Class Description
AutoShowroom
The AutoShowroom Class stores Cars and Buyers in 2 arraylists It also contains all methods used by the I/O menu These methods include creating vehicles, buyers, bids along with displaying cars and buyers
AutoShowroomDriver
Runs the whole Java application Impliments the menu system in console along with accessing all the available methods
Bid
Class which is used to store bid information
BidException
Class for Bid Exceptions which extends Exception
BidsManager
Class which holds a vehicles bids in a HashMap
Buyer
Class which stores Buyer information
Sedan
A class which extends vehicle with added seats attribute
SedanException
Class for Sedan Exceptions which extends Vehicle Exception
Truck
A class which extends vehicle with added capacity and wheels attributes
TruckException
Class for Truck Exceptions which extends Vehicle Exception
Vehicle
Stores vehicles main information and its bids in an instance of the BidManager class
VehicleException
Class for Vehicle Exceptions which extends Exception
